<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> Gambetta, Diego, "Primo Levi's Last Moments", <a href="http://www.bostonreview.net/BR24.3/gambetta.html" class="external free" title="http://www.bostonreview.net/BR24.3/gambetta.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.bostonreview.net/BR24.3/gambetta.html</a> (retrieved on 2008-04-30)</li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2004/08/15/jews_with_tattoos/" class="external text" title="http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2004/08/15/jews_with_tattoos/" rel="nofollow">Jews With Tattoos – Boston Globe Aug 15, 2004.</a></li>
